Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:50.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&H122028&\move(65,113,336,113)\c&H4D5B64&\fnArial}Nepi pred jazdou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:50.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fnArial\3c&H122028&\move(65,540,336,540)\c&H3C474F&}Prosím, sľúb mi to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:52.14,asdf,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\b1\fnArial Narrow\c&H40604F&\pos(680,430)\frz357.659}Naozaj máš rád svojho brata, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemožné! To je smetiak zo supermarketu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Každopádne sa nepribližuj k týpkovi menom Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nerád sa zaoberám Shizu-chanom,\Npretože nerozumie rozumným slovám.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nepovedal som ti, že už nikdy nemáš prísť do Ikebukura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo! Biť sa nie je dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buď ticho!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Najsilnejší v Ikebukure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To musí byť on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiwajima Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyhodili ma bez varovania!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Povedali mi, aby som opustil aj internát!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nedostal som ani odstupné, takže nemám na jedlo alebo na nájomné!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vláda neurobí nič, aby pomohla!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.52,Secondary Thought,,0,0,0,,Buď ticho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, to je vláda! To všetko je vina vlády!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže sa zadlžuješ kvôli hosteske?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je láska!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mint a ja sa naozaj ľúbime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:21.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,Buď ticho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:25.04,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Môžeme sa stretávať len v klube a neviem ani jej číslo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale naozaj sme do seba zaľúbení!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odporné!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vidíte sa len v klube...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevieš ani jej číslo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:36.51,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poviem to priamo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo na tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je skutočná...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Láska!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nenávidím násilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vedel si?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je tam chlapík menom Heiwajima Shizuo, ktorý sa v poslednej dobe úplne prestal ovládať.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten Heiwajima Shizuo je ten, čo nosí barmanskú uniformu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hovorí sa, že bol vždy strašidelný, ale teraz je to s ním vraj ešte horšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ľudia hovoria, že Ikebukuro sa zmenilo na bojovú zónu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už som ho videl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Heiwajima Shizuo je naozaj strašidelný.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zaujímalo by ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemal by si posudzovať ľudí na základe klebiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Setton. Je Heiwajima tvoj kamarát?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno si... taký istý ako on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bojím sa! Zachráňte ma niekto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak to nie je!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra, nemôžem od nikoho zbierať peniaze, pokiaľ ich budeš mlátiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,Smrdí to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vraj sa už dva či tri dni neukázal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto sa v poslednej dobe stáva často...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno je to vďaka tým presláveným únoscom ľudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,Smrdí to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, ľudia boli zranení!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počul som, že to bol Sekáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Práve sa to stalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Videl som to! Ušiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teda...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikebukuro je zase hore nohami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,Smrdí to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:38.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hej, celé mesto smrdí!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,Čo je to, dopekla, za zápach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Toto je odporné!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čau, Shizuo, Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, v poslednej dobe má zlú náladu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shizuo... Je v puberte?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Skôr v rebelantskej fáze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rebelantskej...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, už je to doba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dostal ďalšiu hlavú úlohu, hej?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten Hanejima Yuhei, chcem povedať Heiwajima Kasuka, je teda fakt hviezda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na vášho mladšieho brata musíte byť naozaj hrdý, pán Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, dovoľte, aby som sa predstavil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nielenže dobre vyzerá, ale je to aj dobrý herec, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, ako sa volal jeho prvý film?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, správne
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upírski ninjovia: Carmilla Saizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vedel som, že sa vyšvihne vysoko, keď som ho tam videl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetky kaskadérske kúsky robil sám, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcel by som, aby ste mi povedali, či ste mu pomáhali s tréningom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nenávidím násilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neklamem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vždy som nebol takýto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prvý raz to bolo, keď som sa bil s mladším bratom, Kasukom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hrablo mi kvôli nejakej blbosti, zdvihol som chladničku a skúšal som ju po ňom hodiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niežeby som rozmýšľal nad jej zdvíhaním.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jednoducho sa to nedalo inak, len ju zdvihnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Shizuo, smrdí ti zadok!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hlupák!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nedokázal som sa ovládať.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebol som naštvaný; moje telo sa hýbalo samé od seba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A vždy, keď sa to stalo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ľudia dokážu v extrémnych situáciách šialené veci, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto je asi tvoj prípad, Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mozog šetrí tú silu zničením svalov a kostí, keď dosiahnu limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale tvoj mozog necháva tú silu explodovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môže to byť životná mizéria - ohromujúca udalosť ako žiadna iná!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, dovolíš mi aspoň raz preskúmať tvoje te—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owowowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To bolí!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To bolí, Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neporozumel som detailom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.70,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Zlomí sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Každopádne som to nedokázal ovládať.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.37,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Moja lakťová kosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zlomil by som si telo a všetko okolo mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.03,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Môj pravý lakeť!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toľko som pochopil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prestal som sa pokúšať to ovládať.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V prvom rade nemalo zmysel to vôbec skúšať, ak by som to nedokázal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moje telo sa rozbíjalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako keby mi na tom záležalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moje telo sa zlomilo nespočetne veľakrát a zakaždým zosilnelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako by povedal Shinra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh, aké otravné!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Každopádne som naďalej silnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vždy si zranený, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkaj chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Napi sa mlieka, aby si zosilnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu máš. Aj ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vďaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zašiel som priďaleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A keď som sa spamätal, tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.08,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo to takto dopadlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyrastal som v normálnej rodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neutrpel som žiadnu traumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebojíš sa ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stalo sa to, keď som nastúpil na Rairu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je naša uvítacia ceremónia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetko je výnimočné!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Náš obchod je tu už odjakživa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:38.34,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Asi máme súdené chodiť na tú istú strednú.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buď ticho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako sa drží tvoje telo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne, nechaj ma vyšetriť ťa, aby sme oslávili naše stretnutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak mi dovoľ zobrať ti krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kam si včera išla?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bál som sa, keď si neprišla domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zase si hľadala svoju hlavu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To síce hovoríš, ale stavím sa, že si stretla nejakého fešáka—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prestaň ma udierať do brucha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.04,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Mal som divný pocit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Celty, zoznámim vás...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je môj kamoš, Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.09,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Neviem, ako to mám povedať, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo, Celty býva so mnou alebo by som mal skôr povedať, že je mojou budúc—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.92,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Ona...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aká hrozná spomienka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne, to bolo približne vtedy, keď som stretol tú otravu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tou osobou je... Orihara Izaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto je Orihara Izaya z mojej nižšej strednej.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nuž, nie je to práve dobrý človek... Možno by som mal povedať, že je to hrozný človek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.64,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Nenávidel som ho od chvíle, čo som ho zbadal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty si taký zlý, Shinra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie, nemyslel som to v zlom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemám ho rád.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je smola.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že s tebou bude zábava.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buď ticho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To nehovor, Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vidíš... Toto je zábava, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V deň, čo sme sa stretli... Pokúšali sme sa bojovať na smrť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemal som dôvod, prečo. Jednoducho som ho nemal rád.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je v pohode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je dobre stavaný.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je naozaj v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je v pohode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobrá práca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,Zlyhal som.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, aká náhoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je tu aj Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, prečo nie si zranený?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zabijem ťa! Zabijem ťa! Zabijem ťa! Zabijem ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:40.31,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Ďalší deň bol otravný.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chalani, ktorých som nikdy predtým nevidel, proti mne bojovali jeden po druhom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nič som neurobil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Žil som pokojne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra! Sakra! Sakra! Sakra! Aká otrava!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otravné! Otravné! Otravné! Otravné! Otravné! Otravné!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To bol Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izaya ťahal za všetky nitky v pozadí.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A keď som na to prišiel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IIIzaaayaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keby som ho vtedy zabil...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keď som odpromoval na Raire...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerám dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten idiot tak žil naďalej...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tá otrava robila niečo s Yakuzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Každopádne bolo chvíľu ticho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale aj tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správal sa tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vitajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, videl si?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je ten herec...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanejima Yuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, Kasuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uniforma čašníka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemyslím, že by si mal meniť zamestnania.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doniesol som ti ich veľa... Takže môžeš pokračovať v tom, čo si robil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vďaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nuž, budem sa snažiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten bastard ma dostal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,... a zmizol z Ikebukura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čoskoro zistili, že som nevinný a pustili ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,Prepáč... Nedodržal som sľub.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, ak to nie je Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tom bol na strednej o ročník vyššie odo mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Požiadal ma, aby som mu pomáhal vymáhať dlhy od ľudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stručne povedané, bol som jeho ochranka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Najprv sa mi to nepáčilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tom by povedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nemusíš na ňu tak zodvihnúť ruku."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Mimochodom, Heiwajima Shizuo je so mnou."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nikto mu nemôže stáť v ceste."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,... takéto veci, ale Kasuka mal odvtedy prácu a nevidel som ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,Zaujímalo by ma, či je na mňa naštvaný.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuhei, tadiaľto, prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechápal som prečo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,... ale cítil som sa lepšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stále spolupracujem s Tomom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Termín splatenia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takým komplikovaným veciam nerozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kráčame priamo do záhuby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presne. Škola, spoločnosť, každý má vinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sú srdcom temnoty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Povedal som, že nerozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vypadni odtiaľto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robím si len svoju prácu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo? Čo je to za pohľad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, prečo to máš na sebe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty hlupák, to je sluha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevieš, kto je Shizuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nejaká slávna osoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to pravda, sluha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetko som to vylial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohol by si mi láskavo doniesť ďalší, sluha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fakt sa rútiš do vlastnej záhuby, ak si v Ikebukure a nevieš o Shizuovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moje oblečenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oblečenie, čo mi dal môj brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj tak som nemal veľmi rád násilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcel som zosilnieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Byť dosť silný, aby som ovládal moju zúrivosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cítim sa oveľa lepšie, keď som sa s tebou porozprával.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj? To je skvelé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Celý čas som bol podráždený. Ani neviem prečo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, počula som o tom a bála som sa o teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne? Prepáč, že si sa o mňa musela báť.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pffft. Buď ticho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj keď sa snažím udržať si odstup od cudzincov, neznášam samotu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preto sa pokúšam byť stále v spojení s ľuďmi, ako je Tom a Kasuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie je ako ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiež musí niekoho mať...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už ti skončila puberta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak si daj sushi. Sushi je dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je skvelé!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niekedy inokedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:16.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,Izaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:20.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,To je ono! Vedel som, že tu niečo smrdí!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoj...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,Čo tu robí?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:29.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,Čo má v pláne robiť v tomto meste teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IIIzaaayaaa!
