Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mám sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to dookola ten istý sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spím, keď je to hore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a ono to spí, keď ja som hore.
